<subSubSection pageId="35" pageNumber="142" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="35.[1467,2677,834,2681]" pageId="35" pageNumber="142">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1469,1603,1741,1774]" pageId="35" pageNumber="142">Breeding.</emphasis>
Reproductive season of the Broom Hare occurs in April-September. Females have 1-3 young/litter.
</paragraph>
